### Receiver Service - Event Webhook
### Exemplo de chamada com token de serviço

### 1. Enviar evento COM token válido (deve funcionar)
POST http://localhost:8001/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: secret

{
  "idempotency_key": "unique_key_12345",
  "order_id": "ord_1001",
  "store_id": "store_01",
  "created_at": "2026-02-15T10:15:30"
}

### 2. Enviar evento SEM token (deve retornar 403)
POST http://localhost:8001/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotency_key": "unique_key_123456",
  "event": "order.paid",
  "order_id": "ord_1001",
  "store_id": "store_01",
  "created_at": "2026-02-15T10:18:05"
}

### 3. Enviar evento com token INVÁLIDO (deve retornar 403)
POST http://localhost:8001/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-invalido

{
  "idempotency_key": "unique_key_1234567",
  "event": "order.cancelled",
  "order_id": "ord_1002",
  "order_id": "store_02",
  "created_at": "2026-02-15T11:02:41"
}

### 4. Health check (público, não precisa de token)
GET http://localhost:8001/actuator/health